*bfr-1.6-r1 (14 Jan 2005)

  14 Jan 2005; Matthew Kennedy <mkennedy@gentoo.org> +bfr-1.6-r1.ebuild:
  Resolves a problem where nothing is installed: make DESTDIR=${S} should be
  make DESTDIR=${D}

  16 Dec 2004; Markus Rothe <corsair@gentoo.org> bfr-1.6.ebuild:
  Stable on ppc64

  03 Dec 2004; Tom Martin <slarti@gentoo.org> bfr-1.5.ebuild,
  bfr-1.6.ebuild:
  einstall -> make DESTDIR=${D} install

  04 Nov 2004; Markus Rothe <corsair@gentoo.org> bfr-1.6.ebuild:
  Marked ~ppc64; bug #70048

  10 Oct 2004; Tom Martin <slarti@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Changed <herd> from no-herd to shell-tools@gentoo.org.

  06 Jul 2004; Jeremy Huddleston <eradicator@gentoo.org> bfr-1.6.ebuild:
  ~sparc

  04 Jul 2004; David Holm <dholm@gentoo.org> bfr-1.6.ebuild:
  Added to ~ppc.

  06 Jul 2004; Jeremy Huddleston <eradicator@gentoo.org> bfr-1.6.ebuild:
  ~sparc

  03 Jul 2004; Tom Martin <slarti@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Taking over maintainership as metadata.xml listed this as unmaintained.

